执行序列:
1. @sequential-thinking analyze-problem (问题分析)
2. @serena search_for_pattern (定位代码)
3. @browser-tools reproduce-error (复现错误)
4. @serena find_referencing_symbols (影响分析)
5. 征求修改确认
6. @serena replace_symbol_body (精确修复)
7. @playwright-mcp test (回归验证)
```

